                "name": "Before Combat",
                "text": "The sorcerer casts <i>bear\u2019s endurance</i>, <i>false life</i>, <i>fly</i>, <i>mage armor</i>, and <i>see invisibility</i>."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "During Combat",
                "text": "The sorcerer prefers to fight with her electricity spells, such as <i>chain lightning </i>and <i>lightning bolt</i>, and saves her breath weapon until her foes are lined up so she can catch as many as possible in its effect. She uses spells such as <i>black tentacles</i>, <i>grease</i>, and <i>ice storm </i>to hinder her opponents. If forced into melee combat, the sorcerer casts <i>haste </i>and <i>form of the dragon I</i>."
            },
